title: Jane The Virgin's Justin Baldoni Honors Ashley Tisdale At CoachArt's Gala of Champions
text: Jane The Virgin's Justin Baldoni Honors Ashley Tisdale At CoachArt's Gala of Champions Saturday, 17 October 2015 (13 minutes ago) Ashley Tisdale looks breathtaking in a wine colored dress as she arrives at the 2015 CoachArt ‘Gala of Champions’ held at The Beverly Hilton Hotel on Thursday night (October 15) in Beverly Hills, Calif. The 30-year-old actress was honored at the event by the foundation and good friend, Justin Baldoni. The annual Gala honors individuals [...]
